description: D’Leon’s Taco Truck is an extension of one of Lincoln’s most beloved Mexican restaurants, and it’s roaming the streets and dishing out all their best eats. Their bulging Breakfast Burritos will start your day off deliciously with steak, eggs, and cheese. And if you’re hungry later on, come out again for their yummy Mini Tacos, Carne Asada Burrito or the Grilled Chicken Burrito, if you please. You bring your appetite, they’ll have the lime, now come on out to D’Leon’s Taco Truck for a terrifically tasty time.
name: D'Leon's Taco Truck
